{"tid":1075920,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗迷興用假資料真係過左火，我代表朗迷向一眾美斯迷道歉。","createTime":"2019-03-24T13:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T08:06:09.000Z","uid":173160,"like":50,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"582ffb272daff322b68de8bef06d0c6f3cd3f455","tid":1075920,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/bAvArXJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbAvArXJ.png&h=de459ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好老實，我今朝同好多人一樣，俾個巴打昆左，都信以為真<br />\n但點知俾人踢爆左，身為朗迷都覺得好冇面。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚柒</span></span></strong>。<br />\n我真係覺得果幾位員玩大左。<br />\n搞到今日花朗迷係度嘈成日。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我代表朗迷，向美斯迷道歉。<br />\n我唔求你哋原諒 <br />\n但希望可以平息朗花紛爭。<br />\n我見到你地不停拿C朗來屌，真係好傷心。<br />\n明明係公認世二球星，因為幾粒老鼠屎用假圖，畀你哋講到地底泥咁樣。</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">果幾個劣質朗迷，我真係屌你老母</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b9dc803c8d1d7c30551932b78186429997aea313","tid":1075920,"uid":25831,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9cadec8b0a6c253134c18c12bf9188948d49ccb","tid":1075920,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:18:40.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"d4c6c88630aa6aa2654ae6075ca867cbc8749162","tid":1075920,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9a41d06c3bf0f3011c5d70b5688321d5e02d6e","tid":1075920,"uid":90515,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:50:15.000Z","msg":"好啦原諒你啦，但好似無跟template喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HoCWbMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu